title: ACDC - Immediate Need (2017) ak320
description:
ACDC - Immediate Need (2017)  ak320

Lots of music but with this band that I have been a listener of since Powerage came out.
It was different we got the Album (Vinyl) or Cassette Tape and there it was we listened to them through and through and tracks that were not in "Hot" rotation nevertheless were well known. 
I share a lot of the music I speak of. And I from time to time kick out one of these "The Unknowns" cause they are actually well known to those who are actual listeners of the music.  So enough of my talk you either know what I mean or you don't So to the...

Well I could not Fly completely  under the radar a couple of these were played at shows but not  as much as notable tracks that are Not included on this compilation (Of course thats because they are included in close to Everything else)
If ya liked the ACDC of 80's and 90's I think this will coiver most of it. And if it dont than pick up the 80's 90's of them they are all there
